>  Step To Reproduce:
>
>  	The following steps outline the exploitation of the stored xss vulnerability in  Blood Bank & Donor Management System Project V2.2 application.:
>  
>  	    1.	Launch the Blood Bank & Donor Management System Project V2.2 application.
>  
>  	    2.	Open the signup page by accessing the URL: http://localhost/bloodbank/bbdms/sign-up.php.
>  
>  	    3.	In the Full Name and Message,Address  insert the following Stored xss  payload shown: "><script>alert("1")</script> and signup 
>  
>  	    4.	Click the login button fill username and password and go to "MyAccount" ->  "Profile"
>
>       5.  Now xss will trigger and will popup 
